          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "- Tamas Belgya (in article):",
                " The mean value of 591 +/- 35 b of our total capture",
                "  cross section for 241Am is at the low end of the",
                "  most recent values, but is in agreement with most of",
                "  them within its uncertainty.",
                " The uncertainty is mainly coming from the systematic",
                "  uncertainty of the 242Pu X-ray production probability",
                "  in the electron conversion of the 242Am ground state.",
                "- Tamas Belgya (2012-01-31):",
                " We could measure only the ground state cross section,",
                "  but the MCNP can give only the g+m cross section."
              ]
            }
